---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
const title = 'Guides | pedestrianaccidentcalc.com';
const description = 'In-depth guides covering key topics at pedestrianaccidentcalc.com.';
---
<BaseLayout title={title} description={description}>
  <h1>Guides</h1>
  <p>Plain-language guides written and reviewed by our editorial team.</p>
  <h3><a href="/guides/how-pedestrian-accident-claims-work">How Pedestrian Accident Claims Work</a></h3>
  <p>Insurance coverage, comparative fault, UM/UIM claims, and the settlement process for pedestrian accidents.</p>
  <h3><a href="/guides/pedestrian-accident-fault">Pedestrian Accident Fault and Comparative Negligence</a></h3>
  <p>How fault is allocated between pedestrians and drivers, and how comparative negligence rules affect recovery.</p>
  <h3><a href="/guides/what-to-do-after-pedestrian-accident">What to Do After a Pedestrian Accident</a></h3>
  <p>Immediate steps: medical care, evidence preservation, police report, and finding a personal injury attorney.</p>
  <h3><a href="/guides/pedestrian-accident-misconceptions">Common Pedestrian Accident Misconceptions</a></h3>
  <p>Common misunderstandings about pedestrian accident claims, fault, UM coverage, and settlement values.</p>
  <ul style="margin-top:2rem">
    <li><a href="/case-types">Case types overview</a></li>
    <li><a href="/methodology">Calculator methodology</a></li>
  </ul>
</BaseLayout>
